    {
      "id": "puttimon",
      "displayName": "Puttimon",
      "stage": "Baby I",
      "line": "patamon",
      "spriteFile": "Puttimon",
      "comment": "DIVERGENCE FROM THE SOURCE TREE (US-044). The Digital Monster Color V3 tree (Resources/Digimon_Color_And_Pendulum_Color_Evolution_Trees.md) starts this line at Fresh: Poyomon, but Poyomon exists only as a single 16x16 frame in 'Idle Frame Only/' with no 48x64 animated sheet (verified in docs/sprite-availability.md), so it is dexOnly and may never be playable or named by an edge. Puttimon is substituted as the Baby I: it is the closest animated stand-in, being the Baby I of the same Angel family Patamon belongs to. Poyomon is the ONLY divergence in this line; every other node is the V3 tree as written.",
